item.title: Zips
item.description: Zips allow you, as the name suggests, to quickly zip from one place to another. There are currently two known ways of zipping, jet zips and walljump zips. TODO: add Long Range activation maps and clean this up An explanation of a jet zip can be found here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PoDZUUm0cw0 There’s also this mystery zip https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oQXVp05MLxU
